{"tid":2102013,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（移民台灣）何己完既馬仔JEFF LAM 呃人錢 又周圍恐嚇","createTime":"2020-07-10T07:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T15:21:07.000Z","uid":239389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d87274663b885a9d1c4c2519d25aaa89e8405717","tid":2102013,"uid":239389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:31:16.000Z","msg":"有心想移民台灣既話 一定要小心 FB既群 「台遊達人」<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">JEFF LAM </span></span></strong><br />\n佢係何己完既馬仔 藍到仆街<br />\n見你想移民台灣 無論你想用咩方法移去台灣<br />\n一定會叫你投資移民 再私底下 襯你唔為意<br />\n拎走你既錢 呢到已經有幾個人比JL條友呃錢<br />\n最仆街既係 邊個一講呢件事 佢就去話要告9你<br />\n依家班人忍唔住啦 係台灣到直接告佢 <br />\n一黎無牌 二黎呃錢 三黎恐嚇 <br />\n如果有搵佢幫手搞移民 死硬 即走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AoL5hbk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAoL5hbk.jpg&h=f1fbe150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPgDCbm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPgDCbm.jpg&h=44551180&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07fa977773ea324764779af547dacd262c7a4d81","tid":2102013,"uid":239389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:32:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/taiwantraveller/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftaiwantraveller%2F&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=4d4354ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/taiwantraveller/</a><br />\n大家睇路啦"},{"pid":"46c6d6b581bc89f8d0c99ec936d6bafe0c8aa15c","tid":2102013,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T07:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ac10cad2dfbc726e9b29a682e1aa9783da3d99","tid":2102013,"uid":239389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:21:0